<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Redmine on Shiva Huang Talks</title><link>https://shivahuang.cocoazen.com/tags/redmine/</link><description>Recent content in Redmine on Shiva Huang Talks</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-tw</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2013 00:10:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://shivahuang.cocoazen.com/tags/redmine/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>在Heroku上部署Redmine時的email設定方式</title><link>https://shivahuang.cocoazen.com/posts/2013-08-19-redmine-email-configuration-of-deployment-on-heroku/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 Aug 2013 00:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://shivahuang.cocoazen.com/posts/2013-08-19-redmine-email-configuration-of-deployment-on-heroku/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;最近在Heroku上架了個Redmine，用來練習怎麼使用Heroku和Redmine。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;本來email設定是按照Redmine &lt;a href="http://www.redmine.org/projects/redmine/wiki/EmailConfiguration"&gt;wiki&lt;/a&gt;上教的在&lt;code&gt;config/configuration.yml&lt;/code&gt;中設定如下&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-yml" data-lang="yml"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;production&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;delivery_method&lt;/span&gt;: :&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;smtp&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;smtp_settings&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;address&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;smtp.sendgrid.net&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;587&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;authentication&lt;/span&gt;: :&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;plain&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;domain&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;heroku.com&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;user_name&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;my_email@gmail.com&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;password&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;my_password &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;但如此一來就必須把帳號密碼加入git中，不然無法發佈到Heroku上，但是大家都千交代萬交代不要把密碼commit到版本控制系統中，這不是個好辦法。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>